author: KEXP
title: Cloud Cults Live on KEXP from The Triple Door in Seattle

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Cloud Cult performing live at The Triple Door. Recorded September 14, 2024.

Songs:
When You Reach The End
The Universe Woke Up As You
I Am A Forcefield
Love & The First Law Of Thermodynamics
One Human Being
The Exploding People
You Were Born
Unexplainable Stories
One Way Out Of A Hole
Complicated Creation
There's So Much Energy In Us

Craig Minowa - Guitar, Vocals
Shawn Neary - Bass, Glock, Trombone, Vocals
Sarah Perbix - Piano, Vocals
Shannon Frid-Rubin - Violin, Vocals
Daniel Zamzow - Cello, Vocals
Scott West - Painting, Vocals
Jeremy Harvey - Drums

Host: Kevin Cole
Audio Engineers: Julian Martlew & Sam Schiebner
Audio Mixer: Jeff Johnson
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Emma Juncosa, Jonathan Jacobson & Ettie Wahl
Editor: Jim Beckmann
